- Low. Default path is byte-for-byte unchanged (nil allowlist). Main risk is a
  value-leak regression — mitigated by the grep-assert leak test + reserved-name
  guard. Threading touches several construction sites; a single shared list in
  cli/run.go keeps passthrough and audit in sync.

